<p>Remember, I am a diehard Natural Healing and Herbal Medicine evangelist and I will stop at nothing to try and get you—and your relatives and friends—to heal yourselves naturally, so that is why I do what I do!</p>
<p>Peace,</p>
<p>— Dr. Schulze</p>
