  <p style=''><span style='color:red'>Way to go Dr. Schulze!!!!</span></p>
  <p style=''><span style='color:red'>&mdash;Samantha B.</span></p>
  <hr style="height:1px;width:75%;">
  <p style=''><span style='color:red'>Hurray! Great answer to that imbecilic pseudo - doc. Herbal and
    natural healing is the ONLY way to go!</span></p>
  <p style=''><span style='color:red'>&mdash;Bogdan B.</span></p></i>]]></content:encoded>
